{"tid":840944,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港好多好男仔，只係女仔唔肯俾機會互相了解","createTime":"2018-09-29T07:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T05:22:52.000Z","uid":127052,"like":56,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"69a99f3f8a527716ca4a43cad572474a0a7cfe18","tid":840944,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"我聽過啲仆街嘢<br />\n有啲男人 有個女朋友或者老婆<br />\n鍾意撩女仔傾淫嘢 又抽水又剩<br />\n通常呢啲男人 都識打扮 <br />\n鍾意勾引女人 本身條件唔錯<br />\n容易得到女性歡心 一拖幾件<br />\n結局通常都係中出即飛 <br />\n或者做炮友 唔會諗住認真<br />\n<br />\n其實香港好多好男仔<br />\n可能係宅啲唔識打扮無乜錢<br />\n唔夠膽主動識女仔 或者無乜自信<br />\n但 用情專一 認真 正直 可靠<br />\n唔煙唔酒唔嫖唔賭 <br />\n最多都係鍾意打機同埋睇動漫<br />\n<br />\n如果 香港嘅女仔 學識呢一點<br />\n睇男仔唔好咁片面咁膚淺<br />\n肯花時間去了解一個人嘅為人<br />\n<br />\n就可以趕絕香港啲仆街男"},{"pid":"e9547e86056ce5bb71033f1309f96944878f6dae","tid":840944,"uid":200929,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"你口中所講是毒撚，唔是好男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8aaff671a07c300a0c0adf7d6acc58f10df175","tid":840944,"uid":198165,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"毒撚清貨大平賣"},{"pid":"5f03957d27a3c1544de01a33e1d1a68c3f8d16d1","tid":840944,"uid":125333,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"冇人會鍾意毒撚㗎啦 算啦"},{"pid":"9c2432aef167854160101f7e2afcec12b3b47f55","tid":840944,"uid":138138,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/160007_8ef7558b105c3c161592ac6ea8f9e1bc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F160007_8ef7558b105c3c161592ac6ea8f9e1bc.gif&h=52fa0add&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bc76543e325dc8f5b04fa8c34088a9cfcbe0c33","tid":840944,"uid":90392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"先唔好講話肥同身體唔好, <br />\